review: I've been visiting Delhi Dental Cosmetics for about 1 and a half year for my braces treatment and my experience with this clinic has always been good. I've always got warm welcome and quick registration. And both the doctors i.e Dr. Neha Singhal and Dr. Animesh Aggarwal are really trustworthy for any dental problems. I really praise their work and treatment with thousand mouths. I'm fully satisfied.
Professional and smooth work by the doctor including the whole team of the clinic. Reasonably priced.

Very seamless experience. Highly professional staff and doctors who speak very politely and explain everything very patiently. The best part is that they have very affordable prices, especially for students like me.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,
review:
The doctor is very good and highly experineced. She examines the problem with precision. She is very good at her work. I had gone through RCT treatment for my 3 teeth and it was painfree. 
The Clinic is very hygienic. I would recommend!

The overall experience is really good and satisfying. I'm happy with the results.
I got my braces treatment done from Mrs. Neha Singhal and it turned out really good. I would recommend it to others as well.
An ambience and approach that wins your trust. Very skillful doctors and efficient work. Amiable manner of interaction and concerned suggestions. Patient friendly.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review: It was a very good experience.  Doctors were so friendly nd took care of minute details nd responsive, also the Co ordinating staff is very responsible..
awesome docs nd great behavior... i recommend every patient to go thre....
It was very Nice though I was worried at the start but at the end all turned out to be good
Really educated doctor. I checked out from the clinic with the right consultation
